.landing-container
  .landing-console
    .landing-graybox
      .landing-logo
        %img{:src => "http://i.imgur.com/tTRdWNT.gif"}/
    = form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f|
      .landing-interior
        = f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, class: "sign_in landing different", placeholder: "Email"
        = f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", class: "sign_in landing different", placeholder: "Password"
        %ul.landing-buttons
          %li.landing-login.landing.sign_in
            = f.submit "Log in", class: "allSubmitButtons"
          %br
          %br
    .landing-forgot_password
      =link_to "Sign Up Now!", new_user_registration_path, class: "landing"
  .landing-right
    %h2.landing Sending files. Simplified.
    %p.landing
      File exchange should be a hassle-free part of your business. With T.BOX, files are sent and retrieved via unique URLs. Just log-in, select a box, and upload. Your customers don't need to set up an account to be able to upload into your box. To access your files, all they need is the box's unique URL. Quick and easy.
